title: Colleoni's takes over Rene's on McGregor in Fort Myers
text:
Colleoni's takes over Rene's on McGregor in Fort Myers 
Published By: News-press.com - Today 
Two sisters from Rome are opening an Italian eatery and bakery in the former Rene's space in south Fort Myers ...
